    {
      "allowLineSplit": true,
      "content": "Good typography is invisible. Readers should never notice the grid, the rhythm, or the measure — they should only feel the ease with which meaning reaches them. This document exercises the fundamentals of that craft: paragraph flow, inline styling, alignment, borders, and clean pagination.",
