      "allowLineSplit": true,
      "content": "The border-left treatment derives from manuscript annotation practice: marginalia drawn with a vertical rule to distinguish commentary from the main text. All four borders are active here, padding is asymmetric, and the rule widths differ — a deliberate test of boundary geometry.",
